{"number":130,"verseCount":23,"verses":[[1,["When the Savior shall ",["appear",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Jn. 3:2","nt/1-jn/3.2"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]]," we shall see him as he is. We shall see that he is a ",["man",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature","tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"],"; ",["Man, Potential to Become like Heavenly Father","tg/man-potential-to-become-like-heavenly-father"],"."]]]," like ourselves."]],[2,["And that same ",["sociality",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Family, Eternal","tg/family-eternal"],"; ",["Family, Love within","tg/family-love-within"],"; ",["Marriage, Continuing Courtship in","tg/marriage-continuing-courtship-in"],"."]]]," which exists among us here will exist among us there, only it will be coupled with ",["eternal glory",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Celestial Glory","tg/celestial-glory"],"; ",["Eternal Life","tg/eternal-life"],"."]]],", which glory we do not now enjoy."]],[3,[["John 14:23",["scripture-ref"]],"—The ",["appearing",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Privilege of Seeing","tg/god-privilege-of-seeing"],"."]]]," of the Father and the Son, in that verse, is a personal ",["appearance",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 14:23 (21–23)","nt/john/14.23"],"; ",["D&C 93:1","dc-testament/dc/93.1"],". ",["TG Revelation","tg/revelation"],"."]]],"; and the idea that the Father and the Son ",["dwell",["study-note-ref","c",[["Alma 34:36","bofm/alma/34.36"],"; ",["D&C 130:22","dc-testament/dc/130.22"],"."]]]," in a man’s heart is an old sectarian notion, and is false."]],[4,["In answer to the question—Is not the reckoning of God’s ",["time",["study-note-ref","a",[["Abr. 3:9 (4–10)","pgp/abr/3.9"],"; ",["4:13 (13–14)","pgp/abr/4.13"],"; ",["5:13","pgp/abr/5.13"],". ",["TG Time","tg/time"],"."]]],", angel’s time, prophet’s time, and man’s time, according to the planet on which they reside?"]],[5,["I answer, Yes. But there are no ",["angels",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Angels","tg/angels"],"."]]]," who ",["minister",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 7:6","dc-testament/dc/7.6"],"; ",["43:25","dc-testament/dc/43.25"],"; ",["129:3 (3, 6–7)","dc-testament/dc/129.3"],"."]]]," to this earth but those who do belong or have belonged to it."]],[6,["The angels do not reside on a planet like this earth;"]],[7,["But ",["they",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 18:10","nt/matt/18.10"],"; ",["25:31","nt/matt/25.31"],"; ",["2 Thes. 1:7","nt/2-thes/1.7"],"; ",["D&C 76:21","dc-testament/dc/76.21"],"; ",["136:37","dc-testament/dc/136.37"],"."]]]," reside in the ",["presence",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Tim. 6:16","nt/1-tim/6.16"],"; ",["D&C 76:62, 94 (94, 119)","dc-testament/dc/76.62,94"],"; ",["88:19","dc-testament/dc/88.19"],". ",["TG God, Presence of","tg/god-presence-of"],"."]]]," of God, on a globe ",["like",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ezek. 1:4 (4, 26–28)","ot/ezek/1.4"],"; ",["Hel. 5:23","bofm/hel/5.23"],"; ",["D&C 133:41","dc-testament/dc/133.41"],"; ",["137:2","dc-testament/dc/137.2"],"."]]]," a ",["sea",["study-note-ref","d",[["Rev. 4:6","nt/rev/4.6"],"; ",["15:2 (1–4)","nt/rev/15.2"],"."]]]," of glass and ",["fire",["study-note-ref","e",[["Isa. 33:14","ot/isa/33.14"],"."]]],", where all things for their glory are manifest, past, present, and future, and are continually before the Lord."]],[8,["The place where God resides is a great ",["Urim and Thummim",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Urim and Thummim","tg/urim-and-thummim"],"."]]],"."]],[9,["This ",["earth",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Earth, Destiny of","tg/earth-destiny-of"],"."]]],", in its ",["sanctified",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 77:1","dc-testament/dc/77.1"],"."]]]," and ",["immortal",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Immortality","tg/immortality"],"."]]]," state, will be made like unto ",["crystal",["study-note-ref","d",[["Ezek. 1:22","ot/ezek/1.22"],"."]]]," and will be a Urim and Thummim to the inhabitants who dwell thereon, whereby all things pertaining to an inferior kingdom, or all kingdoms of a lower order, will be manifest to those who dwell on it; and this earth will be ",["Christ’s",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Jesus Christ, King","tg/jesus-christ-king"],"."]]],"."]],[10,["Then the white ",["stone",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Urim and Thummim","tg/urim-and-thummim"],"."]]]," mentioned in ",["Revelation 2:17",["scripture-ref"]],", will become a Urim and Thummim to each individual who receives one, whereby things pertaining to a ",["higher",["study-note-ref","b",[["Abr. 3:3 (3–17)","pgp/abr/3.3"],"."]]]," order of kingdoms will be made known;"]],[11,["And a ",["white stone",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rev. 2:17","nt/rev/2.17"],"."]]]," is given to each of those who come into the celestial kingdom, whereon is a new ",["name",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 62:2","ot/isa/62.2"],"; ",["65:15","ot/isa/65.15"],"; ",["Mosiah 5:12 (9–14)","bofm/mosiah/5.12"],"."]]]," written, which no man ",["",265],"knoweth save he that receiveth it. The new name is the key word."]],[12,["I prophesy, in the name of the Lord God, that the commencement of the ",["difficulties",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 38:29","dc-testament/dc/38.29"],"; ",["45:63 (26, 63)","dc-testament/dc/45.63"],"; ",["87:2 (1–5)","dc-testament/dc/87.2"],". ",["TG War","tg/war"],"."]]]," which will cause much bloodshed previous to the coming of the Son of Man will be in South Carolina."]],[13,["It may probably arise through the slave question. This a ",["voice",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Revelation","tg/revelation"],"."]]]," declared to me, while I was praying earnestly on the subject, December 25th, 1832."]],[14,["I was once praying very earnestly to know the time of the ",["coming",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about","tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]]," of the Son of Man, when I heard a voice repeat the following:"]],[15,["Joseph, my son, if thou livest until thou art eighty-five years old, thou shalt see the face of the Son of Man; therefore ",["let",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 24:36 (36–42)","nt/matt/24.36"],"; ",["D&C 49:7","dc-testament/dc/49.7"],"."]]]," this suffice, and trouble me no more on this matter."]],[16,["I was left thus, without being able to decide whether this coming referred to the beginning of the millennium or to some previous appearing, or whether I should die and thus see his face."]],[17,["I believe the coming of the Son of Man will not be any sooner than that time."]],[18,["Whatever principle of ",["intelligence",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Ne. 9:13 (13–14)","bofm/2-ne/9.13"],"; ",["D&C 93:36","dc-testament/dc/93.36"],". ",["TG Intelligence","tg/intelligence"],"; ",["Learn","tg/learn"],"."]]]," we attain unto in this life, it will rise with us in the ",["resurrection",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Resurrection","tg/resurrection"],"."]]],"."]],[19,["And if a person gains more ",["knowledge",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Education","tg/education"],"; ",["Knowledge","tg/knowledge"],"; ",["Objectives","tg/objectives"],"."]]]," and intelligence in this life through his ",["diligence",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Diligence","tg/diligence"],"."]]]," and obedience than another, he will have so much the ",["advantage",["study-note-ref","c",[["Matt. 25:21 (14–29)","nt/matt/25.21"],"; ",["Alma 12:10 (9–11)","bofm/alma/12.10"],"."]]]," in the world to come."]],[20,["There is a ",["law",["study-note-ref","a",[["Jer. 26:4","ot/jer/26.4"],"; ",["D&C 82:10","dc-testament/dc/82.10"],"."]]],", irrevocably decreed in ",["heaven",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Council in Heaven","tg/council-in-heaven"],"; ",["God, Law of","tg/god-law-of"],"."]]]," before the foundations of this world, upon which all ",["blessings",["study-note-ref","c",[["Ex. 32:29","ot/ex/32.29"],"; ",["Deut. 11:27 (26–28)","ot/deut/11.27"],"; ",["D&C 132:5","dc-testament/dc/132.5"],"."]]]," are predicated—"]],[21,["And when we obtain any ",["blessing",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 6:24","ot/deut/6.24"],"; ",["Alma 45:16 (15–17)","bofm/alma/45.16"],". ",["TG Blessing","tg/blessing"],"."]]]," from God, it is by ",["obedience",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Obedience","tg/obedience"],"."]]]," to that law upon which it is predicated."]],[22,["The ",["Father",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Godhead","tg/godhead"],"; ",["God the Father, Elohim","tg/god-the-father-elohim"],"; ",["Man, Potential to Become like Heavenly Father","tg/man-potential-to-become-like-heavenly-father"],"."]]]," has a ",["body",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 4:24 (23–24)","nt/john/4.24"],"; ",["14:9","nt/john/14.9"],"; ",["Acts 17:28 (25–29)","nt/acts/17.28"],"; ",["Heb. 1:3","nt/heb/1.3"],". ",["TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature","tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"],"; ",["God, Knowledge about","tg/god-knowledge-about"],"; ",["God, Manifestations of","tg/god-manifestations-of"],"."]]]," of flesh and bones as tangible as man’s; the Son also; but the Holy Ghost has not a body of flesh and bones, but is a personage of ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Spirit Body","tg/spirit-body"],"."]]],". Were it not so, the Holy Ghost could not ",["dwell",["study-note-ref","d",[["2 Tim. 1:14","nt/2-tim/1.14"],". ",["TG Holy Ghost, Mission of","tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"],"."]]]," in us."]],[23,["A man may receive the ",["Holy Ghost",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Holy Ghost, Gift of","tg/holy-ghost-gift-of"],"."]]],", and it may descend upon him and not ",["tarry",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Holy Ghost, Loss of","tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"],"."]]]," with him."]]],"volume":"dc"}